# Pinned fnos-mihomo-dashboard release (https://github.com/conversun/fnos-mihomo-dashboard).
# Bump this on every dashboard release — CI rebuilds the fpk on any change to
# this file because it is non-markdown. Override at build time with the
# DASHBOARD_VERSION env var; set to empty / unset to fetch the GH API "latest".
DASHBOARD_VERSION=v0.3.6
